  "B = mu_0*I*r": "",
  "B = mu_0*I^2/r": "",
  "B = mu_0*I/(2*pi*r)": "",
  "For a long straight wire, B = mu_0*I/(2*pi*r). The field decreases inversely with distance and forms concentric circles.": "",
